title: BikeWatch: Boston's Dynamic Bike Traffic Visualizer
description: An interactive geospatial visualization of Boston's bike traffic patterns using Mapbox GL JS and D3.js. Features real-time filtering of 260,000+ bike trips, color-coded traffic flow indicators, and dynamic bike lane overlays. Integrates data from Boston and Cambridge bike networks with BlueBikes station data to reveal urban mobility patterns.
